    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The divine energy coursing through you can empower healing spells. Whenever you or an ally within 5 feet of you rolls dice to determine the number of Hit Points a spell restores, you can spend 1 Sorcery Point to reroll any number of those dice once, provided you don't have the &amp;Reference[incapacitated apply=false] condition. You can use this feature only once per turn.</p><p>Additionally, while under the effect of Innate Sorcery, this range increases to 30 feet and the healing is increased by the spell's level times the Save DC Bonus of your Innate Sorcery.</p>",
